  <brief_title>Treatment of Non-falciparum Malaria</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Artemether Lumefantrine Combination Therapy for the Treatment of Malaria Due to Plasmodium Ovale, Plasmodium Malariae, and Mixed Plasmodium Infections in Gabon</official_title>
