  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with non-falciparum infection will be given artemether-lumefantrine for three days
      and will be followed up for 28 days. Besides efficacy and safety evaluations a substudy on
      immunology will be performed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
